      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Victor, you're coughing a lot.",
      "zh": "Victor，你咳嗽得很厲害。",
      "ja": "ビクター、咳がひどいね。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's take some medicine.",
      "zh": "我們來吃點藥吧。",
      "ja": "薬を飲もう。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't like it. It's yucky.",
      "zh": "我不喜歡，味道很噁心。",
      "ja": "嫌だよ。まずい。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know it doesn't taste good.",
      "zh": "我知道味道不好。",
      "ja": "味が良くないのはわかってるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But it'll make you feel better.",
      "zh": "但它會讓你感覺好些。",
      "ja": "でも、これを飲めば良くなるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And we can take it really fast.",
      "zh": "而且我們可以很快吃完。",
      "ja": "しかもすぐに飲めるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I get some candy after?",
      "zh": "吃完可以吃點糖果嗎？",
      "ja": "飲んだ後にキャンディをもらえる？",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然可以。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You'll get some right after the medicine.",
      "zh": "你吃完藥馬上就能吃糖果。",
      "ja": "薬を飲んだらすぐにあげるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's roleplay.",
      "zh": "我們來角色扮演吧。",
      "ja": "ロールプレイをしましょう。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hahaha!",
      "zh": "哈哈哈！",
      "ja": "ははは！",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you for watching.",
